FBIS3-2030 "drchi043_b_94003" FBIS-CHI-94-043 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Mar 1994 United States & Canada XINHUA Reports U.S. Reinstates Super 301 Trade Law OW0303205194 Beijing XINHUA in English 2032 GMT 3 Mar 94 OW0303205194 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Washington, March 3 (XINHUA) -- U.S. President Bill Clinton signed an executive order here today reinstating the defunct Super 301 trade law, America's ultimate weapon in forcing trade concessions from foreign countries. Speaking at a White House ceremony this afternoon, U.S. Trade Representative Mickey Kantor called the Super 301 a "strong market opening tool."
